    "Initially, when determining the inclusion of an article, we first focus on AI methodologies.",
    "Articles not aligning with AI methods were promptly excluded without further evaluation of other criteria linked to multimodal data fusion or medical/healthrelated issues.",
    "Any article involving technologies associated with machine learning (IA1), DNNs (IA2), or reasoning and metrics (IA3) was classified as AI method-related.",
    "In the subsequent stage, each article categorized as AI method-related underwent assessment for relevance to multimodal data fusion.",
    "Those lacking relevance were excluded outright without consideration of other criteria pertaining to medical/health-related topics."
